{
  "stem": "4753.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That you study the Bible, and when you are 13 years old, you go to the temple.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And before God and before the congregation, you make an oath that from now on, you are responsible for your deed, whatever you do.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you count as a man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my little brother just five months earlier became bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he didn't know where he does belong.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Unfortunately, I told him to go with my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because mothers are the people who take care of sick children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my brother was very, very sick during the four and a half days' trip.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Unfortunately, I didn't know that with my advice, I killed my brother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[CRYING] Because all the children and all the mothers were taken directly to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[CRYING] I didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't know where we are to begin with.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I never could forgive myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as I was standing with my mother and my little brother, I looked to on my father.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father was a six foot, two inch tall, very strong man.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was standing there so miserable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the tears was running on his face.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never saw my father crying like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I didn't even think a moment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I started to run toward him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I wanted to tell him something, comfort him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know what I wanted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe I just wanted to hug him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When halfway through, an SS man stepped forward.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And with a rubber stick what they were always carrying with them, started to beat me and scream at me, go back where you belongs.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, I didn't know that we arrived to Auschwitz-Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
